caption.text: Happy New Year

This year's GPIB Sumber Kasih Christmas Celebration was one of the memorable moments in 2016. After not doing any theatre play at church since a long time ago, I got a chance to do a muted-play and play the role Mary, mother of Jesus Christ, when she was carrying Him on her way to Bethlehem.

It wasn't an easy role and wasn't an easy kind of play; I got no dialogues and only had to do facial expression, which is pretty hard... for me. But, I'm still thankful for everyone who has given their trust for me with this role.

The end of 2016 is finally here. 2016 wasn't an easy year for, I believe, everyone. Let's put aside what has happened in 2016, and be prepared for lots of new adventures in 2017‚ù§

caption.text:
I've been tagged by @nadiadelarosa and @stfn_agatha for this #20factsaboutme thingy. So here are the 20 facts about me. Don't really care if you read this or not.

1. I'm a Christian. Jesus Christ is the love <3
2. "Pengikut Kristus bebas bernyanyi", that's the meaning of my full name which is Christina Fransisca Melodia Tanor.
3. People who just read my name tend to call me "Christine" and I honestly don't like it when people call me that.
4. Had so many nicknames; Christina, Chr, Cher, Cer, Cherina, Kitty, Cherry, Tanor, Yel, Tina, Ntin, Itin -_-
5. May is my month.
6. BLUEEE is my favorite color.
7. Stitch and Superman are my fav.
8. Some people said that when they first met me, my face is so jutek.
9. I'm a cheerful person. (That's what people say)
10. This is my favorite number beside 25.
11. HATE COCKROACHES.
12. I'm a Gemini, but trying to not really become a Gemini.
13. Kata orang "terlalu sabar". Don't know why.
14. Dancing is my passion.
15. Took Performing Arts Communication as my major at STIKOM The London School of Public Relations.
16. Have one little brother who has a very nice voice.
17. Always wanted to climb mountains, but never had a chance to do it.
18. In love with nature and arts.
19. Don't like to have enemies. But if someone hates me, I'll try my best to say sorry even when I'm not the one who makes mistake.
20. I was thinking for not doing this 20facts, but I got bored, so here they are.

There you go my #20factsaboutme. Just do it, it's fun!
